name "f11_scroll_x11"
description "X11 F11 demo: both representations of one physical scroll (core buttons 4/5/6/7 vs XI2 smooth-scroll valuators), XIScrollClass device query, the XIPointerEmulated dedupe flag, and per-gesture totals over a scrollable ruler."
targetType "executable"
sourcePaths "."
importPaths "."
libs "x11" "xi"
targetPath "build"
